Michael Whalen (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Whalen_(actor) 0 Joseph Kenneth Shovlin (June 30, 1902 – April 14, 1974), known as Michael Whalen, was an American actor who starred in B Movies and television, including Son of a Badman and Wee Willie Winkie.
